<a href="/articles/24637.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/24637/indexMediumPc2/24637.jpg?1459233739" alt="内衣在移动拖车里卖，你会想去试一试吗？">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/17/medium/17.png?1411569501" alt="设计">
			<span>设计</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">内衣在移动拖车里卖，你会想去试一试吗？</h1>
